Citation.sTitle: Solubility of Phenacetinum in Methanol, Ethanol, 1-Propanol, 1-Butanol, 1-Pentanol, Tetrahydrofuran, Ethyl Acetate, and Benzene between 282.65 K and 333.70 K
Citation.sAbstract: The solubility of phenacetinum in methanol, ethanol, 1-propanol, 1-butanol, 1-pentanol, tetrahydrofuran, ethyl acetate, and benzene was measured using a laser technique with a temperature range from 282.65 K to 333.70 K. The results of these measurements were correlated with a semiempirical equation.
